<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Sunalta</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
        <p class="par-lg">The serene community of Sunalta is popular for its rich heritage and history, having been founded in the early 1900s. </p>
        <p class="par-xl">It is perfect for individuals looking for a locality that is safe, tranquil, and full of heritage. The neighborhood is well-connected to downtown Calgary.</p>
        <p class="par-lg">The Poplar trees which line the neighborhood stand as a silent tribute to the heritage of Sunalta, making the surroundings peaceful, beautiful and very friendly. </p>
        </div>
